cat << EOF
module-init-tools provides utilities for 
loading and unloading modules on linux 2.5.x

If running for the first time, 
you might want to convert your old
modules.conf to modprobe.conf:

generate-modprobe.conf /etc/modprobe.conf
depmod -a
EOF
